\id COL ALY Alyawarr Bible Northern edition 16 June 19 (Moore) 
\h Colossians 
\toc2 Colossians 
\toc1 Colossians 
\mt1 Colossians  
\mt2 Colossae-areny-rnem-warl  
\imt1 Paul-el pip nhenh thwenek Colossae tawen-areny-rnem-warl  
\ip Ingwerentyel arrwekel-antey tyaty arrernek, Paul-el Colossae-areny tyaty arrerney-angenh. Paul ingkern-they apetyek. Paul ranem atyetyart irrek ikwer-rnemek. Angkakert-rnem ra thwenek ilerl-apayntetyek, Ephesus-areny-rnem ra thwenek. Ephesus ra anenh apmer ilkwa Asia-ampenyel, Rome-areny-rnem atyetyart anenh. Paul-el awenh ingwer-angkwarr, rernem akalty-anthenh, ilpertilenh.  
\ip Akalty-anthey-angker apmwamwam mwanty iterl-arey-angenh anenh. Rernem ament-warl ikwer-rnem-kenh akalty-anthenh. Ingwerentyel ikwer-rnem-kenh-angkwarr apententy, rap itethirretyek-arrpantey arrkernelhem. Arrangkwarlap ran. Aker arlkwey-angenh, alakenh rernem iterrenh. Jesus-kenh-angkwarr apentekerr, arraty inngekety.  
\ip Paul-el pip ikwer-rnem-warl thwenek, renh-rnem akalty-anthayntetyek angka arraty-angkwarr. Jesus Christ-kenh-angkwarrant rernemap itethirreman. Ament-angkwarr akalty-antheyel arrangkwarl, nthakenh itethirrey-angenharl, “Jesus renh tnakenty, ngap itethirreman.” Jesus Christ-elant ingkerrenh itethilem. Ingkartel ahern arrpmernek. Alakenh-they Paul-el angka ikwer-rnem-warl thwenek.  
\c 1
\p
\v 1 Atha Paul thwenek, Ingkartel ayenh arrernek angkakert Christ Jesus-kenh. Timothy-el-then, Ingkart-kenh-angkwarr apenteyel arrpemarl.   
\p
\v 2 Timothy aylanth pip nhenh thwenem arrekantherr-warl, Colossae tawenel aneyel-rnem-warl, iylpareth awelheyel-rnem-warl. Akngey anwekantherrenh Ingkartel arrenhantherrenh mwantyel arntarnt-arem, arrantherr mwerrant-arey anayntetyek.  
\v 3 Anantherr arrekantherr aleth-antey ayerneyel Ingkart Jesus Christ. Ingkartek anwantherr inkwerelheyel, aynikw ikwerenhek.  
\v 4 Anantherr kel awek, arrantherrarl Jesus Christ tnakeyel, arrantherr Ingkart-areny ingkerrenh arntarnt-areyel. Alakenh-anyem anwantherr Ingkartek angkem inkwerelhemel.  
\v 5 Arrantherr Ingkart tnakeyel, rarl arrwekel ilek, arrantherr iteth intem-antey anayntetyek. Arrantherr angka mwerr-angker Ingkart-kenh awenh.  
\v 6 Angka mwerr-angker Ingkart-kenh arlpimpirreyel apmer arrpanenh-warl. Rernem apmer arrpanenhek akalty-antheyel. Rernem tnakek inkwerelhemel. Alakenh-anyem arrantherr angka akwerrpel awenh arrpemarl, “Ingkart ingkerrenhek ilkelheyel” wenh.  
\v 7 Artwa Epaprahas-el arrenhantherrenh akalty-anthenh alakenh, “Ingkart ingkerrenhek ilkelheyel” wenh. Ra Ingkart Jesus-angkwarr warrkerrenh, anwantherr warrkerreyel-apeny.  
\v 8 Ranem arrenhantherrenh akalty-anthenh, Ingkart-kenh Itnwengel arrenhantherrenh akalty-anthenh arrpemarl, ingwer-rnem-itwek mwerrant-arey anayntetyek. Alakenh-they anwantherr angka awek-anem, arrekantherr-penh.   
\p
\v 9-10 Alakenh-anyem anwantherr Ingkart renh-anem ayernek. Anantherr aleth-antey ikwer angkeyel, arrantherr Ingkart-kenh-angkwarr arraty apentetyek, rarl iterreyel-angkwarr, Itnweng Rlwartel arrenhantherrenh akalty-anthetyek, arrantherr arraty iterretyek. Inweng-angkwarr akaltyirreyn-ayntetyek aleth-antey, ingwer-rnem arntarnt-arayntetyek mwerr-angkwarr. Arrantherr artwentyel innga akaltyirretyek angka ikwerenhek.  
\v 11 Ingkartel arrenhantherrenh rlterrkam-rlterrkileyenh. Ingwerentyel arrenhantherrenh apmwewarlilekerr, arrantherr inkwerelhemel aleth apent-ayntetyek ikwerenh-angkwarrant mwerr-angkwarr-ayteng.  
\v 12 Anantherr-anem Akngetyek inkwerelhetyek, rarl angka arrwekel arrernek, arrantherr apmer alker-itwek aney-alpetyek.  
\v 13 Ran anwenhantherrenh apmwekety rakek, rantey arrpemarl alerikw ikwerenh arrernek, Atyetyart anwekantherrenh anetyek, anwantherr ikwerenh-rnem anayntetyek.  
\v 14 Ingkart-kenh alerikw ranem anwekantherr katy ilwek, apmwa anwekantherr-wety iwetyek, anwantherr iteth intem-antey anayntetyek.   
\s1 Alerikw ahern-areny ingkerrenhek anetyek  
\p
\v 15 Anantherr nthakenh Akngey irrwerl-areny arey-angenh. Alerikw ikwerenh atyetyart apmer arrpanenhek. Alerikw retangkwel arrwekel anenh ahern-wenyankel. Alerikw ikwerenh ingkerrenhek anayntirrek-anem, Ingkart anyent rey-antey.  
\v 16 Rlterrk ikwerenhel ra irrwerl-areny-rnem-then ahern-areny-rnem-then arrpmernek. Aleyarl anwantherr areyel-anem. Ikwer-angkwarr inweng-rnem-then ingkerrenh arrpmernek, nthakenh arey-angenh-rnem. Alerikw rlterrk ikwerenh-angkwarr ra ingkerrenh arrpmernek, atyetyart ingkerrenhek anayntetyek.  
\v 17 Alerikw ra kel anenh, ahern nhenh-wenyankel. Ingkartel ahern-areny-rnem-then arrpmerney-angenh-antey, rant anenhan. Alerikwel ingkerrenh-antey atnyeneyel, ahern-areny-rnem ingkerrenh atnyenetyek.  
\v 18 Christ-then Tyaty-areny-rnem anyent-antey, Jesus Christ akapwert-apeny atyetyart aneyel ingkerrenhek. Anyent arlka ikwerenh-apeny anem, inweng anyent-akert rey-antey ikwer-rnem warrkerreyel. Ingkartel renh-tangkwel ipmepenh akemelhilek, alerikw ra ingkerrenhek atyetyart anetyek.  
\v 19 Aray, Ingkartelant alerikw ikwerenh arrernek, ikwer-apeny anayntetyek Ingkart irrkaty-antey ikwer-apeny, anyent rey-antey.  
\v 20 Alerikw ikwer-angkwarr alker-areny ahern-areny ingkerrenh ikwerenh-rnem ayerrpilek. Alerikw ikwerenh arwerl iylpeyl-atherrel ilwemel, ra mwerr-angkwarr mpwarek ingkerrenhek anwantherr apenterl-ayntetyek, mwerrant-arey anayntetyek, arternpel.   
\p
\v 21 Arrantherr Ingkart-wety ament-warl alhenh. Arrantherr apmwangkwarr alhenh ament iterremel, Ingkart-wety arlkarrirrenh.  
\v 22 Alerikw-anem arwerl iylpeyl-atherrel ilwek, arrantherr Ingkart-kenh-angkwarr arraty anetyek. Ra ikwer-warl anyentelhilek, alyelk mwerr anayntetyek, Ingkartel arrenhantherrenh tyatyemeley-angenh.  
\v 23 Arrantherr Ingkart-kenh-angkwarr anetyek, angka mwerr renh rlterrk tnakemel. Arrantherr-anem angkek iylpelirrey-angenh, Ingkartel arrekantherr arrernek, arrantherr iteth intem-antey anayntetyek. Ingkartel ayenh rlwanek, angka mwerr-angker Ingkart-kenh ilerl-apayntetyek ahern-areny ingkerrenhek.   
\p
\v 24 Ayenh apek menty atwem mwerrarl. Christ Jesus arlka menty anthelhek. Ayeng arlka menty anthelhek arrpemarl tyaty-areny ingkerrenhek.  
\v 25 Akngeyel ayenh arrernek, tyaty-areny-rnemek, warrkirretyek, angka ikwerenh ingkerrenhek akalty-anthetyek, ingkerrenhek warrkirretyek.  
\v 26 Arrwekel angka anyelk-tangkwel ayntenh, Aley angka anaynt-anem Ingkart-areny ingkerrenhek, rernem aketh-antey aweyneyel.  
\v 27 Ingkart ilkelheyel, arrantherr Jew-weny-rnem akalty anetyek, angka ikwerenhek, arrantherr apmer mwerr-angker-itwek aney-alpetyek, Christ-kenh-angkwarr.   
\p
\v 28 Rernem-anem Jesus Christ-warl anyentirremel, Jesus Christ tnakeyenh. Anantherr renh-rnem akalty-anthem, rernem arraty-angkwarr apenterl-ayntetyek, ingwer-rnemel renh-rnem ilpertilekerr.  
\v 29 Christ-el ayenh rlterrkileyel. Alakenh-anyem ayeng warrkirreyel, alhengkerr irrey-angenh. Atha ingwer-rnem akalty-anthayntetyek ipmelhey-angenh.   
\c 2
\p
\v 1 Arrantherr iterl-aretyek ayeng arrekantherr warrkirreyel, ingkerrenhek-antey, ingwer-rnem Laodicea tyaty-areny-rnem-then, ayenh iterl-arey-angenh-rnem-then.  
\v 2-3 Arrantherr arnkaty anetyek, mwerrant-arey ingkerrenh anayntetyek. Angka anyelk awank-akerr ayntenh rernem iterl-aretyek. Alakenh-anem ingkerrenh akwerrngel Ingkart-kenh-angkwarr arraty iterl-arayntetyek. Arrantherr Christ-ek akalty anetyek. Christ ra Ingkart-kenh angka ingkerrenhek akalty, arratyant anayntetyek.  
\v 4 Atha arrenhantherrenh arratyant ileyel, ingwerentyel arrenhantherrenh irrtywerremel ilekerr, akaltyel-arrpantey angka ingwer-angkwarr.  
\v 5 Ayeng arrekantherr-itwek aney-angenh arrangkw, ayeng aleth-antey iterreyel arrekantherr. Ayeng inkwerelheyel, atha awekarl, arrantherr arraty apenteyel, Christ rlterrk tnakemel aleth.   
\s1 Jesus anyent impen  
\p
\v 6 Arrantherr Christ Jesus tnakeyel, Ingkart arrekantherr. Kel ikwerenh-angkwarrant apentetyek arrantherr.  
\v 7 Ikwerenh-angkwarrant akaltyirretyek, aleth-antey ikwer angkayntetyek. Renh rlterrk tnakayntetyek, anwantherr arrenhantherrenh akalty-anthek-apeny. Rlterrk tnakayntetyek, iylpelirrey-angenh.   
\p
\v 8 Akalty-arrpantey ingwer-rnem-wety, arrantherr ikwer-rnem-wety arntarnt-arelhetyek, rernem arrenhantherrenh ilpertilekerr apmwewarlilekerr ahern-areny-kenh-angkwarr Christ-kenh-angkwarr-wety akngekerr.   
\p
\v 9 Christ Ingkart anyent rey-antey, inweng anyent-akert.  
\v 10 Christ ra inngarl aneyel anwekantherr-itwel, arrantherr ikwerenh-angkwarr anyentirrek arrpemarl. Christ rey-antey arrpemarl, atyetyart ingkerrenhek aneyel atyetyart ahern-areny-rnemek, irrwerl-areny-rnemek-then.  
\v 11 Arrantherr Jesus Christ-warl anyentirrek, arrantherr apmwangkwarr ahern-areny-kenh-angkwarr apentey-angenh anayntetyek. Apmwamwam ahern-areny-kenh ament arrpemarl. Ra apmwa arrekantherr-wety iwek rlterrk ikwerenhel, arrenhantherrenh itethilek arrpemarl.  
\v 12 Rernem arrenhantherrenh baptise-emilek, arrantherr Jesus Christ-angkwarr aylpem-apeny. Arrantherr ilwem-apeny, arrantherr itethirrem-apeny. Arrantherr itethirrek, Ingkart renh rlterrk tnakemel. Arrantherr Ingkart renh tnakek, rarl Christ renh ipmepenh itethilek  
\v 13 Awank-akerr arrantherr apmwangkwarr-tangkwel apentenh, akwerrp-antey anenh. Arrantherran ipmapeny anenh. Ingkartel arrenhantherrenh itethilek, Christ-angkwarr, apmwa arrekantherr-wety iwek.   
\p
\v 14 Ingkartel anwenhantherrenh menty arek, tyatyemeley-angenh. Apmwa irrarlkek Jesus Christ-el, arwerl iylpeyl-atherrel ilwekel.  
\v 15 Ran arrenty-rnem antengilek arwerl iylpeyl-atherrel ilwemel. Ra arrenty-rnem ywerrelhilek.   
\p
\v 16 Ingwer-rnem apatemel iterreyel Alakenh-anyem rernem angka ingwerek-ingwer ilpertel arrernetyek-arrpantey ahern-areny-kenh-angkwarr, “Nthakenh anwantherr arlkwetyek, nthakenh antywetyek.” Arlta ltyerrey-angker anyentirr-ayntetyek-arrpantey ayntarrp-ileyel.  
\v 17 Ingkart-kenh angka arrwekeleny anwantherr arrwekelant apentenh, alyep, arrkay-apeny. Jesus Christ ranem aremirrek. Aleyan ikwerenh-angkwarrant apenteyel aketh innganem.  
\v 18 Ingwer-rnem arraty-arrpantey tnakelheyel, rernem ilelhem “altyerr areyel” wenh, “antyerl-rnem areyel” wenh. Ikwer-rnem-wety arntarnt-arelhetyek, rernem apal-angkwarr apenteyelarl-wety.  
\v 19 Aray, rernem Jesus Christ renh ipmek. Christ ra tyaty-areny-kenh atyetyart aneyel, akapwert. Alwerrngel arlka anterrkwem. Arlwerrng-akert arlka rlterrk. Arlwerrng-weny arlka thapelirrem, apekap, nthakenh akngelhey-angenh. Arlwerrng-apeny Christ-el ikwerenh-rnem ingkerr anterrkweyel, rlterrkileyel arrpemarl.   
\p
\v 20 Arrantherr Christ-angkwarr anyentirrek-apeny-arrpantey, arrantherr ahern-areny-kenh apenteyel-antey apmwantey. Arrantherr awelheyel ahern-arenyek, rernem arrenhantherrenh ilerl-anenty, “Alakenh mpwareyel” wenh.  
\v 21 Rernem ilem, “Ampwal yanh arney-angenh” wenh, “amern yanh arlkwey-angenh” wenh.  
\v 22 Amern ahern-areny-kenh arwa aynteyel, apmwirrey-angker. Amern arlkwenty, anamerl ywerrem-anem.  
\v 23 Ingwer-rnem iterreyel ikwer-rnem-kenh-angkwarr mwerr-arrpantey. Rernem irrtywerremel ileyel, arraty-angkwarr anetyek-arrpantey. Alakenh-anyem rernem ywarn arratyirretyek-arrpantey arrkernelheyel. Rernem ywarn-antey ilelhem, rernem mwerr-angkwarr anerl-anenty-arrpantey.   
\c 3
\s1 Ingkartel anwenhantherrenh itethilek Christ-angkwarr  
\p
\v 1 Ingkartel arrenhantherrenh itethilek, Jesus Christ-angkwarr. Arrantherr-anem Ingkart-kenh-angkwarr anterr iterretyek, Ingkart-kenh apmerek iterretyek. Christ ra Akngey-itwel aneyel.  
\v 2 Arrantherr-anem anterr iterretyek irrwerl-areny-kenh-angkwarr, ahern-areny-kenh-angkwarr-weny.  
\v 3 Arrantherr ahern-areny-wety ywerrek-apeny, Christ-kenh-angkwarr anyentirremel. Arrantherr innganem Christ-angkwarr intem-antey iteth aney-alpeyenh. Ahern-arenyel arey-angenh, Ingkartelant areyel.  
\v 4 Ingwer-inger Jesus Christ ra apey-alpeyenh rlterrk innga. Ikwer-penh ingwerel-rnem arrenhantherrenh areyenh rlterrk innganem.   
\p
\v 5 Alakenh-anyem arrantherr ahern-arenyek inkwerelhey-angenh. Arrantherr apmwangkwarr alheyel-rnemek inkwerelhey-angenh. Arwa alhewer ingwer alwernirrey-angenh anternetyek, apmwangkwarr iterrey-angenh. Ampwal ingwer-kenhek iterrey-angenh inetyek. Alakenh-anyem Ingkart-kenh-angkwarr irrtywerreyelarl.  
\v 6 Apmwangkwarr alheyel-rnemek Ingkart ahelirreyel.  
\v 7 Awank-akerr arrantherr apmwangkwarrant apentenh.  
\v 8 Aleyan arrantherr apmwangkwarr apentey-angenh. Ingwer-rnemek ahelirrey-angenh, iltey-angenh, irrentey-angenh anetyek.  
\v 9 Arrantherr apmwekety ipmelhek. Arrantherr ingwerek irrtywerrey-angenh.  
\v 10 Arrantherr kel rlengkeny-anem, Jesus-kenh-angkwarr. Ingkartel arrenhantherrenh intem-antey akalty-antheyel, rapeny-anem irretyek, akalty innga irretyek.  
\v 11 Ingkart-kenh-angkwarran arrantherr ingkerr mwerrarl aneyel, apmer ingkerrenh-areny, Jew-rnem-then ingkerrenh, Jew-weny-rnem-then, apmwangkwarr alheyel-rnem-then, warrkenh-rnem-then atyetyart-rnem-then. Mwerrarl anem, anwantherr ikwer-warl anyentirrekarl. Christ ra anwekantherr-itwel aneyel.   
\p
\v 12 Ingkart arrekantherr ilkelheyel ingkerrenhek. Alakenh ra iwerr mpwarek ingkerrenhek arrwekel-antey, ingkerrenhel renh arraty-angkwarr apentetyek, rernem ingwer-rnemek amperrngirretyek atwey-angenh, rernem tnakelhey-angenh ingkerrenh mwerrant-arey anetyek.  
\v 13 Arrantherr iparrp anamerl ahelirrey-angenh. Ingkart-areny ingwerel arrenhantherrenh iltenty, arrantherr renh ilteyney-angenh. Kel menty renh atwey-angenh, Christ-el arrenhantherrenh menty atwey-angenh-apeny.  
\v 14 Kel mwerrant-arey ingkerrenhek anetyek. Ikwer-penh arrantherr anyent-apeny anem.   
\p
\v 15 Arrantherr ingkerrenh arlka anyent-apeny aneyel, Jesus Christ-kenh. Christ-el arrenhantherrenh ayerrpilek, mwerrant-arey ingkerr inkwerelhetyek. Mwerrant-arey atwerrey-angenh anayntetyek, Ingkart ikwer inkwerelhemel.  
\v 16 Christ-kenh angkek iterretyek, arraty akaltyel ingwer-rnem akalty-anthayntetyek, mwerr ilelhemel. Arrantherr aylelhey-angker, psalm-then aylelh-ayntetyek, Ingkartek inkwerelhetyek.  
\v 17 Arrantherr angkerretyek Ingkart-kenh-angkwarr, arrantherr intem-antey Ingkart Jesus-ek iterretyek, Ingkart Akngeyek inkwerelhemel, Jesus-kenh-angkwarr.   
\p
\v 18 Arelh-rnem, artwek awelh-ayntetyek. Alakenh Ingkart-kenh-angkwarr arraty aneyel.   
\p
\v 19 Artwernem, arrantherr anew-rnem mwerr arntarnt-arayntetyek. Arrantherr renh-rnem atwey-angenh.   
\p
\v 20 Ampernem, arrantherr aleth amekengkw aynekengkw awelh-ayntetyek, Ingkartarl ilkelheyel-angkwarr. Ingkart-kenh-angkwarr alakenh aynteyel.   
\p
\v 21 Aynikw-rnem, arrantherr ampernem irrentey-angenh, rernem antwerr alhekerr.   
\p
\v 22 Warrkenh-rnem, arrantherr atyetyart-rnemek awelh-ayntetyek intem-antey, rernem arrenhantherrenh areyel-angkwarr, rernem arrenhantherrenh arey-angenh apal aneyel-angkwarr. Ingkartel areyel. Ingkartek mwerr warrkirr-ayntetyek.  
\v 23 Arrantherr iylpareth iytekerr-antey atnwentirrey-angenh warrkirretyek Ingkartek, ahern-arenyek warrkirrey-angenh.  
\v 24 Arrantherr kel akalty, Ingkart rarrp arrenhantherrenh ilek-ilek antheyenh apmer ikwerenh-itwek. Arrantherr Ingkart Christ ikwer warrkirrey-alpeyenh.  
\v 25 Ingkart anyentekant ilkelhey-angenh, ingkerrenhek ilkelherl-ayntetyek. Ingkartel ingkerrenh arraty tyatyemileyel.   
\c 4
\p
\v 1 Atyetyart-rnem, arrantherr warrkenh-rnem mwantyel arntarnt-aretyek, ilek-ilek arraty anthayntetyek. Arrantherr atyetyart arrekantherrenh iterl-areyel, irrwerl-they areyelarl-wety.   
\s1 Akngey ayernetyek ipmelhey-angenh  
\p
\v 2 Intem-antey Ingkart-warl angkerl-ayntetyek, ikwer arraty iterr-ayntetyek, ikwer inkwerelhetyek.  
\v 3 Arrantherr Ingkart-warl angketyek, ra ingkerrenh iylpa altyweriletyek, ingkerrenhel angka Christ-kenh arraty awetyek. Angka anyelk-tangkwel ayntenh. Angka atha ilerl-apenh arwa alhewer. Ingwer-rnem arlkarrirrenh, alakenh ayenh rernem tyayel-warl akwernek.  
\v 4 Arrantherr Ingkart renh ayernenherr-arey, ra ayenh rlterrkiletyek, atha angka anyelk-penh arraty anayntiletyek ingkerrenhek.   
\p
\v 5 Arrantherr akwerrp-rnem angka ikwer akalty-anthetyek, rernem iterl-arayntetyek arrpemarl.  
\v 6 Arrantherr arternp ilayntetyek ikwer-rnem. Rernem arrenhantherr ayernenty, arrantherr renh-rnem arraty iletyek.   
\p
\v 7-8 Artwa Tychicus-el ra atyenh aneyel arrpemarl, Ingkartek iylpareth. Ra Ingkartek warrkirreyel arrpemarl. Athanem renh arrekantherr-warl thwenem, ra atyeng-iperr ingkerrenhek iletyek, arrenhantherrenh arternpiletyek, atyeng iterrerl-anekerr.  
\v 9 Onesimus atha thwenem arrpemarl arrekantherr-warl. Ratherr atherrel-antey angka anwekantherr-iperr iletyek.   
\p
\v 10 Aristarchus ra atyeng-itwel aneyel arrpemarl, tyayl-itwek. Ra angka thwenem arrpemarl. Ingwer-rnemel angka thwenem arrpemarl Mark ikwer-penh, Barnabas-kenh ankelikw. Ra apetyenty, arrantherr ikwer inkwerelhem arrpemarl.   
\p
\v 11 Jesus itnan ingweran Justus. Artwa Jew irrpety rernemant Jesus Christ renh tnakeyel arraty. Rernem anwekantherr-itwek warrkerreyel. Rernem anwenhantherrenh arternpileyel.   
\p
\v 12 Epaphras arrekantherrenh arrpemarl apmer nhak-areny, Jesus Christ-kenh warrkenh arrpemarl \em Hallo\em* angkeyel arrpemarl. Ra rlterrk aleth Ingkart ayerneyel, ipmelhey-angenh, arrenhantherrenh rlterrkiletyek, arrantherr arraty-angkwarr apenterl-ayntetyek.  
\v 13 Ayeng akalty, ra arrekantherr iterreyel aleth, tyaty-areny-rnem ingkerrenhek, Laodicea-areny-rnemek, Hierapolis-areny-rnemek.   
\p
\v 14 Arntety mwerreley-angker wethey, Luke-el angka thwenem arrpemarl, Demas-el angka thwenem arrpemarl.   
\p
\v 15 Laodicea tyaty-areny-rnem iletyek arrpemarl, “Ayeng iterreyel arrekantherr” wenh, arelh Nympha arrpemarl, ingwer-rnem-then meeting-ek akarrirreyel ikwer-warl.   
\p
\v 16 Arrantherr pip nhenh reytemiletyek arrpemarl. Arrantherr pip nhenh thwenem Laodicea-areny-rnem-warl, rernem reytemiletyek arrpemarl. Arrantherr pip reytemiletyek arrpemarl. Pip atha arrwekel thwenek Laodicea-warl, arrantherr reytemilemel aretyek, iterl-aretyek.   
\p
\v 17 Artwa Archippus iletyek, “Ingkartek warrkirretyek angka ikwerenh ywerrelhiletyek, akalty-anthemel, rarl ngkweng arrernek-angkwarr-antey.”   
\p
\v 18 Ayeng inkwernelheyel angka atyenh, Paul. Atyeng iylpangkenh-arey, ayengarl tyaylel aneyelek. Ingkartel arrenhantherrenh mwantyel arntarnt-arem.  
\p Kel-antey.   